snippet: Fremont is one of a handful of cities to take independent action over the past decade to restrict illegal immigration.
abstract: Residents of Fremont, Neb, vote to keep regulations requiring all renters to swear they have legal permission to live in United States.
lead_paragraph: Fremont is one of a handful of cities to take independent action over the past decade to restrict illegal immigration.
